@startuml
title Budget and Transaction Activity

|User|
start
:Open dashboard;

|Application|
:Load selected month and year;

|User|
if (Budget exists for month?) then (No / add budget)
  :Enter budget amount,\nmonth, and year;

  |BudgetService / WalletDatabase|
  :Validate positive amount;
  :Validate month and year;

  if (Budget is valid?) then (yes)
    |SQLite|
    :Insert budget or add to\nexisting monthly budget;

    |Application|
    :Refresh dashboard balance;
  else (no)
    |Application|
    :Show budget validation error;
    stop
  endif
endif

|User|
:Enter transaction amount,\ncategory, month, and year;

|TransactionService / WalletDatabase|
:Validate amount, month, and year;
:Load monthly budget;

if (Monthly budget exists?) then (yes)
  if (Amount is within remaining budget?) then (yes)
    |SQLite|
    :Insert transaction;
    :Deduct amount from budget balance;

    |Application|
    :Refresh dashboard and transaction list;
    :Show saved message;
    stop
  else (no)
    |Application|
    :Show over-budget error;
    stop
  endif
else (no)
  |Application|
  :Show missing-budget error;
  stop
endif
@enduml
